  <brief_title>The Influence of Coping Strategies and Catastrophizing on Patients With Back and Neck Pain</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Influence of Coping Strategies and Catastrophizing on Patients With Back and Neck Pain Treated Within the Spanish National Health Service</official_title>
